IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: SKYLINE KIWANIS IS A CHAPTER OF KIWANIS INTL AND IS A GLOBAL ORGANIZATION OF VOLUNTEERS DEDICATED TO IMPROVING THE WORLD, ONE CHILD AND ONE COMMUNITY AT A TIME. WE CONDUCT VARIOUS FUNDRAISERS THAT ARE OPEN TO THE PUBLIC TO RAISE MONEY FOR OTHER NON PROFITS IN THE COMMUNITY AND TO HELP INDIVIDUALS WITH A DEMONSTRATED NEED. WE ALSO VOLUNTEER OUR TIME ROUTINELY WITH VARIOUSNON PROFITS SUCH AS MEALS ON WHEELS AND SALVATION ARMY. NO MEMBER IS COMPENSATED FOR THEIR WORK IN THE CLUB.

IRS990.Desc: BINGO: ONCE A WEEK THE CLUB HOSTS A BINGO SESSION WITH VARIOUS GAMES BROKEN DOWN IN SCHEDULE G. EIGHTY PERCENT OF THE NET PROCEEDS OF THESE SESSIONS ARE DONATED TO FOUR LOCAL CHARITABLE ORGANIZATIONS. THE REMIAING TWENTY PERCENT IS DONATED TO THE SKLYLINE KIWANIS FOUNDATION WHICH THEN DONATES MONEY TO VARIOUS CHARITABLE CAUSES IN THE COMMUNITY. PERIODICALLY SKYLNE KIWANIS SUPPORTS KIWANIS INTERNATIONAL BY GIVING DUES.
